Hi John, 
The first command was unable to execute (invalid topic type 1). The second command moved the robot a little and then I was able to do the playback. 

I have a rosnode that gets commands over the network and then sends the messages on "/atlas/joint_commands" "sandia......left..../joint_commands" and same for the right hand. I tried running the rosnode as a bare linux executable or with rosrun and both fail as soon as I publish to even "/atlas/joint_commands"
